    "chapter": {
        "bookTitle": "D&C",
        "delineation": "Section",
        "number": 91,
        "summary": "1\u20133, The Apocrypha is mostly translated correctly but contains many interpolations by the hands of men that are not true; 4\u20136, It benefits those enlightened by the Spirit.",
        "chapterAugmentations": [],
        "verses": [
            {
                "text": "Verily, thus saith the Lord unto you concerning the Apocrypha\u2014There are many things contained therein that are true, and it is mostly translated correctly;",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "BD\u00a0Apocrypha.",
                        "start": 52,
                        "end": 61
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "There are many things contained therein that are not true, which are interpolations by the hands of men.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Record Keeping; Scriptures, Preservation of.",
                        "start": 69,
                        "end": 83
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "Verily, I say unto you, that it is not needful that the Apocrypha should be translated.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "D&C 45:60 (60\u201361); 93:53.",
                        "start": 76,
                        "end": 86
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "Therefore, whoso readeth it, let him understand, for the Spirit manifesteth truth;",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Understanding.",
                        "start": 37,
                        "end": 47
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "And whoso is enlightened by the Spirit shall obtain benefit therefrom;",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Holy Ghost, Mission of; Inspiration.",
                        "start": 32,
                        "end": 38
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "And whoso receiveth not by the Spirit, cannot be benefited. Therefore it is not needful that it should be translated. Amen.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            }
        ]
    }
}